title: Player Attack S03E17 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
This week, I get my hands dirty with an Early Access look at Killing Floor 2, the latest from Tripwire Interactive - and trust me when I say it's not just a clever name.

If you're a crazy cat lady (or have well-hidden crazy cat lady tendencies), Mel has a roundup of games that should make you happy when you're away from your feline friends - and Jonny Robot's off to the cinema. Grab the popcorn, he's got some opinions about Mad Max: Fury Road, and he's gonna tell anyone who'll listen.

Plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news - this is Player Attack!
